YC_K33G_rzzhidYYdpim9OcaZC6YQbhPJkqUIpf-NYtNw&oe=66E183E7"}, {"file_name": "Screenshot 2024-04-23 105539.png", "id": "1227799471525515", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57568676_1227799474858848_7768688368680066198_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=WqGmW6j_GtkQ7kNvgHqlKnZ&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=ARlPgIGgGlb_2VDHZ7WcVxW&oh=00_AYCR0Q3vCASRL2LrsGD_Ft2pr1yO3bMPBrKRkXl-C2sHbw&oe=66E177CA"}, {"file_name": "Screenshot 2024-04-23 105213.png", "id": "7267932849999757", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035456_7267932856666423_2080840504819002250_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=bhvv_vUFNEoQ7kNvgHjBWHV&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=ARlPgIGgGlb_2VDHZ7WcVxW&oh=00_AYAf7GU526fJCx8U8Bg0BgOAEp0Jn5hSylugT0dginq94A&oe=66E18D14"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Scared Chimp", "keywords": [], "long_description": "In the confines of the research facility, amidst the cold metal and artificial light, a scared chimp resides, its once vibrant spirit subdued by the weight of captivity. Each day unfolds in a monotony of routines, its fur dulled and its movements marked by hesitancy as it navigates the sterile enclosure. Through the bars of its cage, it gazes longingly towards a world it can no longer touch, yearning for the freedom of its natural habitat. Yet, despite the fear that grips its trembling frame, there remains a flicker of resilience, a silent plea for understanding in the depths of its wide, expressive eyes. In this delicate balance between captivity and longing, the scared chimp serves as a poignant reminder of the ethical complexities inherent in the pursuit of knowledge and the profound bond that unites all living beings in a shared journey of empathy and compassion.", "short_description": "In the confines of the research facility, amidst the cold metal and artificial light, a scared chimp resides, its once vibrant spirit subdued by the weig